# Checklist: Pull Request Review

> **When to use:** When reviewing or creating a pull request.
> **Applies to:** All code changes before merge.
> **Update Trigger:** Modify when review requirements or PR templates change.

## PR Author Checklist

Complete before requesting review:

### Code
- [ ] All tests pass locally
- [ ] New tests added for new functionality
- [ ] Lint and type checks pass
- [ ] No unrelated changes included
- [ ] Code follows existing patterns

### Documentation
- [ ] PR description explains what and why
- [ ] Breaking changes documented
- [ ] API changes reflected in docs/schemas
- [ ] Complex logic has comments

### Testing
- [ ] Happy path tested
- [ ] Error cases tested
- [ ] Edge cases considered
- [ ] No flaky tests introduced

### Security
- [ ] No secrets in code
- [ ] Input validation present
- [ ] Auth checks where needed
- [ ] OWASP top 10 considered

